301
00:18:18,137 --> 00:18:19,597
Kau takkan bisa dilacak.

302
00:18:39,325 --> 00:18:40,368
Tutup pintunya.

303
00:18:43,371 --> 00:18:44,830
Jangan dibuka kalau begitu.

