345
00:21:32,373 --> 00:21:34,875
- Turun.
- Di sini?

346
00:21:35,918 --> 00:21:37,294
Ini uang perjanjian kita.

347
00:21:38,212 --> 00:21:40,881
Selalu cek ponselmu,
aku tak menelepon dua kali.

348
00:21:43,467 --> 00:21:44,885
