"Mulai tertarik padaku?"

354
00:22:17,251 --> 00:22:20,045
"Sudah kubilang aku benci dikekang."

355
00:22:21,714 --> 00:22:23,090
Mereka sangat keren.

356
00:22:25,926 --> 00:22:27,011
Aku mau...

357
00:22:27,469 --> 00:22:29,763
Aku mau ke kamar mandi sebentar.

358
00:22:35,769 --> 00:22:36,770
Itu bagus.

359
00:22:49,533 --> 00:22:51,827
<i>Jadi, kesimpulannya,</i>

360
00:22:51,910 --> 00:22:55,706
<i>kini dia bisa masuk markas Argos
